If someone else comes across this same issue as I did, the solution for me was that I had not paid attention to the location of the following lines: 
"{% load leaflet_tags %}
{% leaflet_js plugins="forms" %}
{% leaflet_css plugins="forms" %}"

Make sure "{% load leaflet_tags %}" is before the <html> opening tag.

Also make sure "{% leaflet_js plugins="forms" %}
                           {% leaflet_css plugins="forms" %}" is located in the <head> section of your HTML.

This solved the problem for myself.

Good luck!

